###########################################################
avhrr2mitiff
###########################################################

AUTHOR:
Øystein Godøy, METNO/FOU, 22.02.2008

PURPOSE:
To read AVHRR imagery in various format using libfmutil and libfmio and
convert these to MITIFF format for subsequent viewing in DIANA or
splitting using satsplit.

REQUIREMENTS:
  o libfmutil
  o libfmio
  o libproj (not if libfmutil is built without PROJ support)
  o libtiff
  o libhdf5 (not if libfmio is built without HDF5 support)

BUILD INSTRUCTIONS:
  1. Edit Makefile
  2. make

NOTES:
Very simple interface, will be replaced in time with other functionality.
